There are also: photographs of mission houses; visitors book;
		  photographs of local activity and items of furniture made in mission workshops;
		  photographs of local modes of transport; photographs of church building and of
		  local activities; 
		Amapinda Mwa Kubelenga Abaichye, a book of childrens
		stories by W. Freshwater; 
		Umwa Kubelenga Ifintu Fya Mu Cipingo Ca Kale, a book of
		bible stories; and, circa 200 envelopes sent from Central Africa to the UK with
		the original postage stamps and the franking of African postal stations.
